ly expensive therapy lamp but it’s also covered by a 10-year warranty, which is one of the best we&#39;ve seen. Only the <a href=\"/sunlight-jr-review\">Sunlight Jr.</a> has a stronger warranty.","The Amjo Sun BRIGHT Sun Lamp does not come with a visible clock, timer or adjustable intensity settings. You will need to move the lamp closer or farther away to adjust intensity and turn the machine off when your session is done.","The simplicity of this sun lamp doesn&#39;t hinder its performance. You can run this LED-powered lamp while you read the morning newspaper or when you first arrive at the office without taking up a lot of space on your table or desk. The full 10,000 lux lights provide enough power for most light therapy programs, and the lack of individual features does not diminish the overall effect."]},"id":"9dd4bf44-774f-45b4-95f5-ee08e9de84a1","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_64168","url":"/amjo-sun-bright-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeph-preece","url":"/author/jeph-preece","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Jeph Preece","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"UEqrRM5xmXnCHCjkbS6o5e","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-04-14T21:09:45Z","datePublished":"2015-04-14T21:09:45Z","name":"Amjo Sun BRIGHT","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":56,"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","language":"en","dateModified":"2017-08-11T00:00:00Z","id":"PbbCu2qriqWFnhwioeBUqi","meta":{"title":"Amjo Sun BRIGHT Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Amjo Sun BRIGHT is a powerful LED lamp for treating SAD, mood and sleep disorders. Learn more about it in our review."},"products":[{"slug":"amjo-sun-bright","url":"/product/amjo-sun